For write (i.e., create, update, or delete) operations, you may specify a value between 0 and 255 inclusively, [0, 255]. - PRODUCT_ACTION_TYPE,

- BROWSER_SIZE, 
- PLATFORM, 
- PLATFORM_VERSION, 
- LANGUAGE, 
- SCREEN_RESOLUTION, 
- SCREEN_COLORS,

- FLASH_VERSION, 
- GEO_SPEED (Connection speed), 
- VISITOR_TYPE,

- GEO_IP_ADDRESS, 
- GEO_IP_VERSION,

- GEO_REGION, 
- GEO_CITY,   
- Event  
- EVENT_CATEGORY, 
- EVENT_ACTION, 
- EVENT_LABEL,

- CUSTOM_FIELD_2, 
- USER_DEFINED_VALUE,   
- Application  
- APP_ID, 
- APP_INSTALLER_ID, 
- APP_NAME, 
- APP_VERSION, 
- SCREEN, 
- IS_APP (Boolean Field), 
- IS_FATAL_EXCEPTION (Boolean Field), 
- EXCEPTION_DESCRIPTION,

- SOCIAL_ACTION,
